        "title": "fix(agents): retry compaction with backup auth profiles",
        "body": "## Summary\n- retry native compaction with the next same-provider auth profile when an auto-selected profile hits retryable rate-limit/overload failures\n- keep user-selected auth profiles locked so manual profile choices are not silently replaced\n- stop profile failover if the transcript leaf changes between attempts, avoiding retrying compaction after state drift\n\nFixes #53531\n\n## Validation\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/compact.hooks.test.ts` (72 tests passed)\n- `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p test/tsconfig/tsconfig.core.test.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/core-test.tsbuildinfo`\n- `node scripts/check-session-accessor-boundary.mjs`\n- `./node_modules/.bin/oxlint --tsconfig config/tsconfig/oxlint.core.json src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/compact.ts src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/compact.types.ts src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/compaction-runtime-context.ts src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/compact.queued.ts src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run.ts src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/compact.hooks.test.ts src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/compact.hooks.harness.ts`\n- `git diff --check`\n\n## Notes\n- `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p tsconfig.core.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/core.tsbuildinfo` currently fails on latest `main` in `src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/tool-result-context-guard.ts` because `CONTEXT_LIMIT_TRUNCATION_NOTICE` is unused. This file is outside this PR's diff.\n",
